  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.10.2">
<l>karaiyāy kākkaippiḷḷāy</l>
<l>karumāmukil pōlniṟattaṉ</l>
<l>uraiyār tolpuka ḻuttama ṉaivarak</l>
<l>karaiyāy kākkaippiḷḷāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Caw, baby crow;</l>
<l>The one whose hue is like a huge, dark cloud,</l>
<l>The supreme whose ancient fame [sacred] words spread,</l>
<l>Caw [for him] to come, baby crow!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
